 Command: 

1. Go to project folder
cd project

2. Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv

3. Activate it:

Windows:

venv\Scripts\activate

Mac/Linux:

source venv/bin/activate

4. Install all dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

5. Set database connection:

Windows (PowerShell):

$env:DATABASE_URL="mysql+pymysql://user:password@localhost:3306/metroblue"

Mac/Linux:
export DATABASE_URL="mysql+pymysql://user:password@localhost:3306/metroblue"

6. Train the model (Intern A)
python lead_scoring/train.py

7. Run the API (Intern C)
uvicorn main:app --reload

8. Test in browser
Swagger UI 
http://127.0.0.1:8000

Lead scoring API:
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
Use POST /api/leads/score

Revenue (Intern B dummy):
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/revenue/forecast

9.Run tests
pytest
